<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="462" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1436,535,704]" pageId="10" pageNumber="462">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,335,572,597]" pageId="10" pageNumber="462">Comments.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation box="[342,498,572,597]" pageId="10" pageNumber="462" refId="ref8740" refString="Mayor, A. (2007) Family Dasytidae. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Smetana, A. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 4. Elateroidea, Derodontoidea, Bostrichoidea, Lymexyloidea, Cleroidea, Cucujoidea. Apollo Books, Stenstrup, pp. 388 - 415." type="book chapter">Mayor (2007)</bibRefCitation>
gives “ 
<collectingCountry box="[581,631,572,596]" name="Iran" pageId="10" pageNumber="462">Iran</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[642,690,573,596]" name="Iraq" pageId="10" pageNumber="462">Iraq</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[700,782,572,597]" name="Turkey" pageId="10" pageNumber="462">Turkey</collectingCountry>
” as distribution, most likely as circumscription of the 
<typeStatus box="[1388,1436,573,597]" pageId="10" pageNumber="462">type</typeStatus>
locality. However, 
<bibRefCitation box="[374,558,607,632]" pageId="10" pageNumber="462" refId="ref9523" refString="Schilsky, J. (1897) Die K a fer Europa's. Nach der Natur Beschrieben. Heft 34. von Bauer und Raspe (E. Κuster), Nurnberg, viii + 54 pp. [viii pp. + 100 nr. (each on 1 or 2 sheets) + nr. 34 A- 34 G (= 54 pp.)]" type="book">Schilsky (1897)</bibRefCitation>
specifies “russisches 
<collectingRegion box="[821,931,607,632]" country="Iran" name="Kordestan" pageId="10" pageNumber="462">Kurdistan</collectingRegion>
(Kasikoporan)” as 
<typeStatus box="[1168,1216,608,632]" pageId="10" pageNumber="462">type</typeStatus>
locality. The 
<typeStatus box="[1388,1436,608,632]" pageId="10" pageNumber="462">type</typeStatus>
locality is spelled today as Kazkoparan or Kozkoparan, and lies in north-western 
<collectingCountry box="[1075,1155,644,669]" name="Turkey" pageId="10" pageNumber="462">Turkey</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion box="[1170,1338,644,669]" country="Turkey" name="Igdir" pageId="10" pageNumber="462">Igdir province</collectingRegion>
). We are not aware of a published record for 
<collectingCountry box="[551,596,680,703]" name="Iran" pageId="10" pageNumber="462">Iran</collectingCountry>
or 
<collectingCountry box="[634,683,680,703]" name="Iraq" pageId="10" pageNumber="462">Iraq</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
